Interface DataLoader.LoadingListener<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - after postprocessing of the loaded data an object of type T will be created and passed into processFinished(Request, byte[], Object)
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LoadingAdapter
    Enclosing class:
    DataLoader<T>

    public static interface DataLoader.LoadingListener<T>
    Listener interface for loading (uploading and downloading) process.

    • Method Detail

      • processStarted

        void processStarted(Request request)
        Called before the loading process started. Process can be divided into uploading and downloading (HTTP POST and GET), or just downloading (other protocols).
        Parameters:
        request - Request that is processed now

      • uploadingUpdateProgress

        void uploadingUpdateProgress(Request request,
                           long uploadedBytes,
                           long totalBytes)
        Called while the params are uploaded.
        Parameters:
        request - Request that is processed now
        uploadedBytes - total bytes that have already been uploaded
        totalBytes - total bytes that should be uploaded (sum of all params sizes)

      • downloadingUpdateProgress

        void downloadingUpdateProgress(Request request,
                             long loadedBytes,
                             long totalBytes)
        Called while the data is downloaded.
        Parameters:
        request - Request that is processed now
        loadedBytes - total bytes that have already been downloaded
        totalBytes - total bytes that should be downloaded (content length)

      • processFinished

        void processFinished(Request request,
                   byte[] rawData,
                   T data)
        Called when the loading had been successfully finished.
        Parameters:
        request - Request that had just successfully finished
        rawData - raw downloaded data
        data - postprocessed loader-specific data

      • processFailed

        void processFailed(Request request,
                 java.lang.Exception e)
        Called when the loading has failed (both while uploading and downloading).
        Parameters:
        request - Request that had just failed
        e - raised Exception
